data.name: Office_Action_Description
data.value: Ikhlayenti ye-imeyili eshonile eyenziwe ukufinyelela ngokushesha futhi ikhokhovulele ukuxhumana.

data.name: Office_Assure_Description
data.value: Lula ukuphathwa kwesibopho nokulungiswa ngokusebenzisa uhlelo oluqondene nolwazi.

data.name: Office_Booking_Description
data.value: Hlela izikhathi zokuhlangana futhi hlela ikhalenda yakho ngephulatifomu yethu ethandwa yabasebenzisi.

data.name: Office_Clock_Description
data.value: Lungisa isikhathi sakho ngephrogramu yokuphathwa kwesikhathi, isibekeli sesikhathi, nesiqinisekiso esihlangabezana.

data.name: Office_Duplicare_Description
data.value: Phinda futhi gcina izincwadi zokugcina zokuphrinta ngesixhumanisi sokukopisha esisebenza kahle.

data.name: Office_Filer_Description
data.value: Hlela, faka ukufinyelela, bese uphatha amafayela nezinkomba zakho zedijithali ngokusebenza kahle.

data.name: Office_Globe_Description
data.value: Thola amaphethelo, hlela izindlela, bese uqhakambisa idatha yezwe ngezibaluli ezinemininingwane.

data.name: Office_Have_Description
data.value: Ukulandelela izimpahla ngokunembile ukuze kube nokuphathwa okuhle kwezihlangu kanye nokulawula kwemali.

data.name: Office_Jupiter_Description
data.value: Finyelela futhi uqhakambise amawebhusayithi ngokuphepha ngesivinini esiphezulu kanye nokusebenza okuhle.

data.name: Office_Lead_Description
data.value: Khipha ukuthengiswa nokuxhumana kwabathengi ngesoftware yethu yezindlela zokusebenza ezingaphezu kwezidingo.

data.name: Office_Merchant_Description
data.value: Phatha ibhizinisi lakho lokuthenga ngezandla ngesistimu yethu yokubeka okwenziwe kahle.

data.name: Office_Nerve_Description
data.value: Sebenzisa ubuchwepheshe bemfundo ezenziwe kahle ukuseshwa okwenziwe kahle, ukutholakala kwesiqophi, kanye nokuqondiswa kwesiko.

data.name: Office_Operate_Description
data.value: Landela futhi uqondise amahora emsebenzi ngesisombululo sethu sokulandela isikhathi esizwakalayo.

data.name: Office_Qapture_Description
data.value: Faka, gcina futhi yabelana ngamaqophi ngesisombululo sokugunda okusetshenziswa kahle.

data.name: Office_Repo_Description
data.value: Buyisela amakhumbula ahleliwe ngokulula ukubuyisela izithombe eziyosusiwe ngendlela yethu.

data.name: Office_Soap_Description
data.value: Gcina ikhompyutha yakho isebenze kahle ngekhlini yethu efanelekayo.

data.name: Office_Voice_Description
data.value: Shintsha umbhalo ojwayelekile ukuba ngamazwi akhuluma nezwi elinjalo kanye nezilungiselelo ezingaguqulwa.

data.name: Office_Wealth_Description
data.value: Qondisa izinqubo zokubhalisa nokukhokha ngesisindo sethu sezezimali esilula ukusetshenziswa.

data.name: Office_Xhibit_Description
data.value: Umhlaziyi wokubuka izithombe kanye nohleli oluphelele, okuphelele kubaphotografi.

data.name: Office_Yield_Description
data.value: Imikhankaso yokuthengisa nge-imeyili ebalulekile ukukhulisa ubuningi bakho futhi ukudlulisela ubuqotho.

data.name: Office_Mia_Description
data.value: Umncedisi oqedwa ngobuchwepheshe bemfundo engenakulungiswa ngezilimi zemvelo.
